{"schema":"allo-reading-book@1","slug":"110883-water-dance","title":"Water Dance","description":"Guddu can dance to anything. Today he has found music in water and can’t stop doing a jig as he makes his way down a stream. A story that introduces water bodies and celebrates the joy of water.","language":"English","langCode":"en","isRtl":false,"level":"1","orientation":"landscape","authors":["Sean D'mello"],"illustrators":["Ajanta Guhathakurta"],"originalAuthors":[],"publisher":"Pratham Books","license":"CC BY 4.0","licenseUrl":"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/","sourceId":"storyweaver","contentType":"story","source":{"id":"storyweaver","name":"StoryWeaver, Pratham Books","url":"https://storyweaver.org.in/en/stories/110883-water-dance"},"cover":{"card":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/721324/size3/5a1f19ca4a60e1aaf734bc03f0c3be11.jpg","large":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/721324/size6/5a1f19ca4a60e1aaf734bc03f0c3be11.jpg"},"audio":null,"pages":[{"n":1,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/158303/size6/8ce08903cf1db92bd9e238c29e123231.jpg","text":"Guddu loves to dance. He dances to the cow mooing and to the sound of someone eating.","words":null},{"n":2,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/158304/size6/c808e8783698d341e805403d39d7feb0.jpg","text":"Drip Drip\nDrop Drop Drop\nGush Gush!\n“Water, you are full of beats!\nLet’s see what else you can do.”","words":null},{"n":3,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/158305/size6/66da9bdec4e5776651b7e05df72e9d4d.jpg","text":"Swish Swosh Swish Swosh\n“Slow down, stream!\nI can’t keep up with you.”","words":null},{"n":4,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/158306/size6/70d97bed9817cac58f97a305a737fad7.jpg","text":"Burble Burble\nBurble Burble\n“I wonder if a river would have a gentler beat! I could bounce about with the river.”","words":null},{"n":5,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/158308/size6/317375323b57e24b555f3ba70ff58f46.jpg","text":"Whoosh Boom Bash\n“The ocean may look calm, but the waves must be wild and loud!”","words":null},{"n":6,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/158307/size6/40e7b25912d7db9d802abe61632c08e0.jpg","text":"Paf Paf Paf Paaaf\n“Nothing can be louder than this rain! These raindrops are quick and fast.”","words":null},{"n":7,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/158309/size6/334536deefd2df4c2001e528798e35b4.jpg","text":"Whoosh Fizz,\nWhoosh Fuzz\n“Oh waterfall, you\nare quite loud too!”","words":null},{"n":8,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/158311/size6/a5362f750de79e6766de2c79ec6bf274.jpg","text":"“Mom is skipping stones by the pool.\nMaybe the pool has a tune too?”","words":null},{"n":9,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/158457/size6/1641260eb39d0155c85e4e9e49b07c80.jpg","text":"Skippety\nSkippety Skippety\nPlop","words":null},{"n":10,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/158458/size6/9e02833516090eb37c0ae43ee4517f44.jpg","text":"“Why are you dancing, Guddu?” everyone asks. “There’s no music.”\n“There is music and there is rhythm. Just listen to the water!”","words":null},{"n":11,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/158459/size6/8cf9ae97df1ff07146bbb00a5b030bfd.jpg","text":"12/12","words":null}],"stats":{"pages":11,"words":156}}